   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"To Flavius Phoibammon, logistes of the Oxyrhynchite nome, from Aurelius Timotheos and Pekyllos of the same city. Aurelius Aion who lives in the same village as we do . . . and he wrote, handing it over to your goodness, and accused us and ensured that we were locked up as if we had committed the theft . . . " (TC)</ab>
         </div>
